// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0337 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bdc890fb-3db6-548c-b4c0-d86e7cbdf647

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
